  <entry>
    <title>next常见配置功能插件</title>
    <url>/2020/06/12/hexo/next%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD-%E5%BE%85%E5%AE%8C%E5%96%84/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h3 id="评论功能"><a href="#评论功能" class="headerlink" title="评论功能"></a>评论功能</h3><p>leanCode+valine</p>
<h3 id="置顶功能"><a href="#置顶功能" class="headerlink" title="置顶功能"></a>置顶功能</h3><p>修改hexo-generator-index插件，hexo文件目录中，把<code>node_modules/hexo-generator-index/lib/generator.js</code>中代码替换为：</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#39;use strict&#39;;</span><br><span class="line">var pagination &#x3D; require(&#39;hexo-pagination&#39;);</span><br><span class="line">module.exports &#x3D; function(locals)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  var config &#x3D; this.config;</span><br><span class="line">  var posts &#x3D; locals.posts;</span><br><span class="line">    posts.data &#x3D; posts.data.sort(function(a, b) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        if(a.top &amp;&amp; b.top) &#123; &#x2F;&#x2F; 两篇文章top都有定义</span><br><span class="line">            if(a.top &#x3D;&#x3D; b.top) return b.date - a.date; &#x2F;&#x2F; 若top值一样则按照文章日期降序排</span><br><span class="line">            else return b.top - a.top; &#x2F;&#x2F; 否则按照top值降序排</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        else if(a.top &amp;&amp; !b.top) &#123; &#x2F;&#x2F; 以下是只有一篇文章top有定义，那么将有top的排在前面</span><br><span class="line">            return -1;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        else if(!a.top &amp;&amp; b.top) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            return 1;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        else return b.date - a.date; &#x2F;&#x2F; 都没定义按照文章日期降序排</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">  var paginationDir &#x3D; config.pagination_dir || &#39;page&#39;;</span><br><span class="line">  return pagination(&#39;&#39;, posts, &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    perPage: config.index_generator.per_page,</span><br><span class="line">    layout: [&#39;index&#39;, &#39;archive&#39;],</span><br><span class="line">    format: paginationDir + &#39;&#x2F;%d&#x2F;&#39;,</span><br><span class="line">    data: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      __index: true</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>博文添加，top值越大越靠前</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: next功能待完善</span><br><span class="line">date: 2020-06-12 21:13:35</span><br><span class="line">tags: </span><br><span class="line">- next</span><br><span class="line">categories:  </span><br><span class="line">- 其他</span><br><span class="line">top: 1000 # top值越大越靠前</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>添加置顶标签，修改文件<code>./themes/next/layout/_macro/post.swig</code>，在<code>&lt;div class=&quot;post-meta&quot;&gt;</code>添加如下代码</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% if post.top %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fa fa-thumb-tack&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;font color&#x3D;7D26CD&gt;置顶&lt;&#x2F;font&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;span class&#x3D;&quot;post-meta-divider&quot;&gt;|&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endif %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="代码复制"><a href="#代码复制" class="headerlink" title="代码复制"></a>代码复制</h3><h3 id="顶部加进度条"><a href="#顶部加进度条" class="headerlink" title="顶部加进度条"></a>顶部加进度条</h3><blockquote>
<p>切换到文件夹的<code>/themes/next</code>文件夹下，执行以下命令</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;theme-next&#x2F;theme-next-pace source&#x2F;lib&#x2F;pace</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>进入next的配置文件<code>_config.yml</code>中设置</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Progress bar in the top during page loading.</span><br><span class="line">pace: true &#x2F;&#x2F;开启进度条</span><br><span class="line"># Themes list:</span><br><span class="line">#pace-theme-big-counter</span><br><span class="line">#pace-theme-bounce</span><br><span class="line">#pace-theme-barber-shop</span><br><span class="line">#pace-theme-center-atom</span><br><span class="line">#pace-theme-center-circle</span><br><span class="line">#pace-theme-center-radar</span><br><span class="line">#pace-theme-center-simple</span><br><span class="line">#pace-theme-corner-indicator</span><br><span class="line">#pace-theme-fill-left</span><br><span class="line">#pace-theme-flash</span><br><span class="line">#pace-theme-loading-bar</span><br><span class="line">#pace-theme-mac-osx</span><br><span class="line">#pace-theme-minimal</span><br><span class="line"># For example</span><br><span class="line">pace_theme: pace-theme-center-simple &#x2F;&#x2F;进度条样式</span><br><span class="line"># pace_theme: pace-theme-minimal</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="3D标签"><a href="#3D标签" class="headerlink" title="3D标签"></a>3D标签</h3><p>Hexo博客Next主题建立标签云hexo-tag-cloud及效果展示<br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/aoman_hao/article/details/89416634" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.csdn.net/aoman_hao/article/details/89416634</a></p>
<h3 id="修改背景图"><a href="#修改背景图" class="headerlink" title="修改背景图"></a>修改背景图</h3><blockquote>
<p>修改<code>themes\next\source\css\_custom\custom.styl</code>文件</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 添加以下代码，添加背景图片</span><br><span class="line">body &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    background:url(https:&#x2F;&#x2F;source.unsplash.com&#x2F;random&#x2F;2560x1440);</span><br><span class="line">    background-repeat: no-repeat;</span><br><span class="line">    background-attachment:fixed;</span><br><span class="line">    background-position:50% 50%;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


<h3 id="修改文章底部标签样式"><a href="#修改文章底部标签样式" class="headerlink" title="修改文章底部标签样式"></a>修改文章底部标签样式</h3><p>修改<code>hexo\themes\next\layout\_macro\post.swig</code>中文件，<code>command</code>+<code>f</code>搜索<code>rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#</code>，将#替换成<i class="fa fa-tag"></i></p>
<h3 id="右下角添加宠物"><a href="#右下角添加宠物" class="headerlink" title="右下角添加宠物"></a>右下角添加宠物</h3><p>1、切换到博客项目的根路径，执行以下命令</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -save hexo-helper-live2d</span><br><span class="line">npm install live2d-widget-model-wanko(主题可选如下)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>2、mac OS安装时出现错误</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">gyp: No Xcode or CLT version detected!</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>3、解决办法，参考<a href="https://lbb-1011.gitee.io/2020/06/14/Mac%20OS/npm/#more" target="_blank" rel="noopener">npm执行报错</a>，然后执行步骤1<br>4、在hexo的<code>_config.yml</code>中添加如下参数</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">live2d:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  scriptFrom: local # 默认</span><br><span class="line">  pluginRootPath: live2dw&#x2F; # 插件在站点上的根目录(相对路径)</span><br><span class="line">  pluginJsPath: lib&#x2F; # 脚本文件相对与插件根目录路径</span><br><span class="line">  pluginModelPath: assets&#x2F; # 模型文件相对与插件根目录路径</span><br><span class="line">  tagMode: false # 标签模式, 是否仅替换 live2d tag标签而非插入到所有页面中</span><br><span class="line">  debug: false # 调试, 是否在控制台输出日志</span><br><span class="line">  model:</span><br><span class="line">    use: live2d-widget-model-wanko</span><br><span class="line">  display:</span><br><span class="line">    position: right</span><br><span class="line">    width: 145</span><br><span class="line">    height: 315</span><br><span class="line">  mobile:</span><br><span class="line">    show: false # 是否在移动设备上显示</span><br><span class="line">    scale: 0.5 # 移动设备上的缩放</span><br><span class="line">  react:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>步骤1、步骤4可选值</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">live2d-widget-model-chitose</span><br><span class="line">live2d-widget-model-epsilon2_1</span><br><span class="line">live2d-widget-model-gf</span><br><span class="line">live2d-widget-model-haru&#x2F;01 (use npm install --save live2d-widget-model-haru)</span><br><span class="line">live2d-widget-model-haru&#x2F;02 (use npm install --save live2d-widget-model-haru)</span><br><span class="line">live2d-widget-model-haruto</span><br><span class="line">live2d-widget-model-hibiki</span><br><span class="line">live2d-widget-model-hijiki</span><br><span class="line">live2d-widget-model-izumi</span><br><span class="line">live2d-widget-model-koharu</span><br><span class="line">live2d-widget-model-miku</span><br><span class="line">live2d-widget-model-ni-j</span><br><span class="line">live2d-widget-model-nico</span><br><span class="line">live2d-widget-model-nietzsche</span><br><span class="line">live2d-widget-model-nipsilon</span><br><span class="line">live2d-widget-model-nito</span><br><span class="line">live2d-widget-model-shizuku</span><br><span class="line">live2d-widget-model-tororo</span><br><span class="line">live2d-widget-model-tsumiki</span><br><span class="line">live2d-widget-model-unitychan</span><br><span class="line">live2d-widget-model-wanko</span><br><span class="line">live2d-widget-model-z16</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>5、重新启动项目</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>6、删除主题，删除<code>hexo/node_modules/hexo-helper-live2d</code>文件夹，修改<code>hexo/package.json</code>文件，删除live2d相关内容</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  &quot;dependencies&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;hexo&quot;: &quot;^4.2.1&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;hexo-deployer-git&quot;: &quot;^2.1.0&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;hexo-helper-live2d&quot;: &quot;^3.1.1&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;live2d-widget-model-haruto&quot;: &quot;^1.0.5&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;live2d-widget-model-wanko&quot;: &quot;^1.0.5&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">    &quot;live2d-widget-model-z16&quot;: &quot;^1.0.5&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>










]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>其他</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>next</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>壁纸网站</title>
    <url>/2020/06/14/%E5%A3%81%E7%BA%B8%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="不只是Unsplash-–-免费高清图片-照片素材网站分享（多图）"><a href="#不只是Unsplash-–-免费高清图片-照片素材网站分享（多图）" class="headerlink" title="不只是Unsplash – 免费高清图片/照片素材网站分享（多图）"></a>不只是Unsplash – 免费高清图片/照片素材网站分享（多图）</h1><hr>
<h2 id="免费超高清照片素材站"><a href="#免费超高清照片素材站" class="headerlink" title="免费超高清照片素材站"></a>免费超高清照片素材站</h2><p>照片素材一般用于制作网页背景、宣传海报、banner或 是写博客文章的时候比较常用。</p>
<p><img src="https://img.liaosam.com/uploads/2016/06/89.jpg" alt="89"></p>
<hr>
<p><a href="https://unsplash.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://unsplash.com/</a><br>收藏多年的免费超高清图片素材网站，每张图片都特别唯美，料网很多文章图片也来自于此站。该网站的图片没有任何版权问题，你可以放心使用。Unsplash 是一个真正免费高质量照片的网站，主打风景图片，照片分辨率也很大，用来做网页素材已经足够，该照片网站每10天更新10张照片。<code>如果打开慢，请自行FQ。</code></p>
<p><a href="https://www.gratisography.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.gratisography.com/</a><br>每周定期发布一些高品质的免费照片，数量没有 Unsplash 多，每周更新，以后也会越来越多。</p>
<p><a href="https://stocksnap.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://stocksnap.io/</a><br>好站不用多解释。</p>
<p><a href="https://picography.co/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://picography.co/</a><br>和 unsplash 一样，都是心头爱之一。</p>
<p><a href="https://abduzeedo.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://abduzeedo.com/</a><br>每日创意灵感分享</p>
<hr>
<p><a href="https://www.pexels.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.pexels.com/</a><br>pexels free stock photos。支持按颜色找照片。</p>
<p><a href="https://www.designerspics.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.designerspics.com/</a><br>可作为设计素材的照片</p>
<p><a href="https://foter.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://foter.com/</a><br>海量免费高清图片</p>
<p><a href="https://pixabay.com/en/editors_choice/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://pixabay.com/en/editors_choice/</a><br>Pixabay，几十万张免费无版权限制的照片、背景图片、矢量文件和艺术插图</p>
<hr>
<p><a href="https://raumrot.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://raumrot.com/</a><br>图库质量不错</p>
<p><a href="https://morguefile.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://morguefile.com/</a><br>跟上面站都差不多类型的。免费下载。</p>
<p><a href="https://wefunction.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://wefunction.com/</a><br>免费高清照片，网页图标，图片素材等</p>
<p><a href="https://picjumbo.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://picjumbo.com/</a><br>分免费个人使用和商业使用，图片质量不错</p>
<p><img src="https://img.liaosam.com/uploads/2016/06/70.jpg" alt="70"></p>
<hr>
<p>上面发的都是免费的，还有几个不错的付费站：</p>
<p><a href="https://500px.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://500px.com/</a><br>国外高质量摄影照片网站（付费）</p>
<p><a href="https://www.istockphoto.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.istockphoto.com/</a><br>同上类似（付费）</p>
<p><a href="https://www.dreamstime.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.dreamstime.com/</a><br>同上类似（付费）</p>
<hr>
<h2 id="特色免费高清图片站"><a href="#特色免费高清图片站" class="headerlink" title="特色免费高清图片站"></a>特色免费高清图片站</h2><p><a href="https://magdeleine.co/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://magdeleine.co/</a><br>如果说 Unsplash 是主打风景，Magdeleine 则主打黑白图片，但也有别的颜色。而且有一个特色功能，它可以按照你选择的颜色或者你的情绪，帮你寻找图片。</p>
<p><a href="https://foodiesfeed.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://foodiesfeed.com/</a><br>网站主打美食高清图，看着流口水，根本没办法减肥。</p>
<p><a href="https://www.textures.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.textures.com/</a><br>国外超全的各种材质纹理的背景图</p>
<hr>
<h2 id="设计图片素材站（有些要付费）"><a href="#设计图片素材站（有些要付费）" class="headerlink" title="设计图片素材站（有些要付费）"></a>设计图片素材站（有些要付费）</h2><p><a href="https://www.shutterstock.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.shutterstock.com/</a><br>国外高清设计图库。前面 Sam 有写过一篇 <a href="https://www.liaosam.com/get-great-pictures-based-on-shuttershock.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">如何免费使用 shutterstock 图片</a></p>
<p><img src="https://img.liaosam.com/uploads/2015/10/shutterstock-factory2.jpg" alt="shutterstock-factory2"></p>
<p><img src="https://img.liaosam.com/uploads/2015/10/shutterstock-global-market.jpg" alt="shutterstock-global-market"></p>
<p><img src="https://img.liaosam.com/uploads/2015/10/shutterstock-business.jpg" alt="shutterstock-business"></p>
<p><img src="https://img.liaosam.com/uploads/2015/10/presentation.jpg" alt="presentation"></p>
<p><img src="https://img.liaosam.com/uploads/2015/10/shutterstock-UAV.jpg" alt="shutterstock-UAV"></p>
<p><img src="https://img.liaosam.com/uploads/2015/10/factory1.jpg" alt="factory1"></p>
<p><img src="https://img.liaosam.com/uploads/2015/10/factory2.jpg" alt="factory2"></p>
<p><img src="https://img.liaosam.com/uploads/2015/10/factory3.jpg" alt="factory3"></p>
<p><a href="https://www.pixelsquid.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.pixelsquid.com/</a><br>去背景的3D图片素材</p>
<p><a href="https://dribbble.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://dribbble.com/</a><br>设计师们的最爱，看过没有不说好的</p>
<p><a href="https://www.canva.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.canva.com/</a><br>超屌的图片设计素材站。浏览器太落后的可能访问不了。用谷歌账号登入，可以在线设计矢量图等。适合有一定美工功底或喜欢折腾的人。</p>
<p><img src="https://img.liaosam.com/uploads/2016/06/85.jpg" alt="85"></p>
<hr>
<h2 id="来几个国内的："><a href="#来几个国内的：" class="headerlink" title="来几个国内的："></a>来几个国内的：</h2><p><a href="https://www.zcool.com.cn/gfxs/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.zcool.com.cn/gfxs/</a><br>站酷</p>
<p><a href="https://www.quanjing.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.quanjing.com/</a><br>全景图库。国内人气较高的版权图库</p>
<p><a href="https://huaban.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://huaban.com</a><br>花瓣</p>
<p><a href="https://creative.vcg.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://creative.vcg.com/</a><br>视觉中国。刚收购了 CorbisImages（比尔盖茨创建的视觉创意内容机构）</p>
<p><a href="https://www.sccnn.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.sccnn.com/</a><br>素材中国</p>
<p><a href="https://www.lanrentuku.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.lanrentuku.com/</a><br>懒人图库  不只是图片，很多网页特效的 JS 源码</p>
<p><a href="https://www.nipic.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.nipic.com/</a><br>昵图网，这个不用多介绍了。图片大排档。。</p>
